<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        /* Base Resets */
        body, table, td, a { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
        table, td { mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; }
        img { -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; border: 0; height: auto; line-height: 100%; outline: none; text-decoration: none; }
        
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            body, .email-wrapper { background-color: #0f0b1f !important; }
            .email-container { background-color: #1a1333 !important; border-color: #2b1f55 !important; }
            .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #6d28d9) !important; }
            .content, .reminders { color: #e5e7eb !important; }
            .content h2, .content p strong { color: #ffffff !important; }
            .summary-box { background-color: #2a1f4a !important; border-color: #6d28d9 !important; }
            .summary-title { color: #c4b5fd !important; }
            .accent-text { color: #a78bfa !important; }
            .notes-text { color: #9ca3af !important; }
            .button { background-color: #8b5cf6 !important; }
            .footer { background-color: #0f0b1f !important; color: #9ca3af !important; }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="email-wrapper" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f8fafc; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;">
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 20px;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table class="email-container" width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"
                    style="max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
                    
                    <tr>
                        <td class="header" style="background: #3dd16a; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3dd16a 0%, #2eb357 100%); padding: 40px; text-align: center;">
                            <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">FridgeNet</h1>
                            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #ffffff; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Community Support System</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td class="content" style="padding: 40px; color: #1e1b2e; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px;">
                            <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e1b2e; font-size: 22px;">Donation Scheduled!</h2>
                            <p>Hi <strong>{{ full_name }}</strong>,</p>
                            <p>Thank you for contributing to the community. Your donation helps keep our local fridges stocked for those who need it most.</p>

                            <div class="summary-box" style="background-color: #f3f0ff; border: 1px solid #ddd6fe; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
                                <h3 class="summary-title" style="margin-top: 0; color: #339614; font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.2px; font-weight: 700;">
                                    Drop-off Summary
                                </h3>

                                <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="font-size: 15px;">
                                    <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;"><strong>Fridge:</strong> {{ fridge_name }}</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;"><strong>Item:</strong> {{ item_name }}</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;"><strong>Quantity:</strong> {{ quantity }}</td></tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td style="padding: 4px 0;">
                                            <strong>Drop-off Date:</strong>
                                            <span class="accent-text" style="color: #339614; font-weight: bold;">{{ dropoff_date }}</span>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>

                                {% if notes and notes.strip() %}
                                <div style="margin-top: 15px; padding-top: 15px; border-top: 1px dashed #ddd6fe;">
                                    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #339614; font-weight: bold;">YOUR NOTES:</p>
                                    <p class="notes-text" style="margin: 5px 0; font-style: italic; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">"{{ notes }}"</p>
                                </div>
                                {% endif %}
                            </div>

                            <p><strong>Quick Reminders:</strong></p>
                            <ul class="reminders" style="padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Ensure items are factory-sealed or properly labeled.</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Check the "Use By" dates before dropping off.</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Place items neatly inside the fridge.</li>
                            </ul>

                            <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                                <tr>
                                    <td align="center">
                                        <a href="{{ url_for('map_page', _external=True) }}"
                                           class="button"
                                           style="background-color: #3dd16a; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(61, 209, 106, 0.3);">
                                           View Fridge Map
                                        </a>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td class="footer" style="background-color: #1e1b2e; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; color: #a4aebc; font-size: 12px;">
                            <p style="margin: 0; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">&copy; 2026 FridgeNet. Supporting local communities together.</p>
                            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">You received this email because you scheduled a donation.</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>